<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="tight-adv">tight <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /taɪt/    美 /taɪt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>紧紧地；充分地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Shut</strong> the door <strong>tight</strong>. 
把门关紧。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Sleep tight</strong>!
睡个好觉！</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>tighten /'taɪtn/ v <br />
tightly /'taɪtli/ adv   </p></div>